child-realistic model at $k=1024$. Performance degradation at large $k$ is
more pronounced than for GPT-2 XL, particularly for low-frequency RCs,
suggesting the smaller model is more susceptible to retrieval noise.}
\label{fig:app_context_child_k1024}
\end{figure*}

